00:08:34,014 --> 00:08:36,224
<font face="Serif" size="18">They're not idiots, Grandpa. They're me.</font>

160
00:08:36,307 --> 00:08:41,104
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ha. You'll know how funny that is when
we get back. I had your father picked up.</font>

161
00:08:41,187 --> 00:08:42,897
<font face="Serif" size="18">- He's over there.
- What? Why?</font>

162
00:08:42,981 --> 00:08:46,026
<font face="Serif" size="18">I thought you'd be grateful
and less distracted than if I let him die.</font>

163
00:08:46,109 --> 00:08:49,112
<font face="Serif" size="18">- He's been in real bad shape since he lost his wife.
- My mom?</font>

164
00:08:49,195 --> 00:08:51,740
<font face="Serif" size="18">Your not-at-all-real mom in a video game,</font>

165
00:08:51,823 --> 00:08:54,075
<font face="Serif" size="18">occupied by a tiny fraction of yourself.</font>

166
00:08:54,159 --> 00:08:56,494
<font face="Serif" size="18">A fraction of yourself which is now dead forever,</font>

167
00:08:56,578 --> 00:08:58,913
<font face="Serif" size="18">and fractions add up,
so I had your dad brought here.</font>

168
00:08:58,997 --> 00:09:01,249
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're welcome, you heartless monster.</font>

169
00:09:01,332 --> 00:09:03,043
<font face="Serif" size="18">Marta. It's me, Dad.</font>

170
00:09:03,126 --> 00:09:04,461
<font face="Serif" size="18">I converted for you.</font>

171
00:09:04,544 --> 00:09:06,629
<font face="Serif" size="18">My name is Morty. So is yours.</font>

172
00:09:06,713 --> 00:09:09,591
<font face="Serif" size="18">There's no conversion. We're Morty. It's a fact.</font>

173
00:09:09,674 --> 00:09:13,386
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sure. Anything you say.
I don't wanna fight. I'm proud of you.</font>

174
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:16,306
<font face="Serif" size="18">Are you mad at me because
before you became the most powerful woman,</font>

175
00:09:16,389 --> 00:09:19,350
<font face="Serif" size="18">I shamed you for your haircut
