265
00:13:30,685 --> 00:13:33,354
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Good.
- But you have to tell us you love us.</font>

266
00:13:35,315 --> 00:13:38,651
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>At this point even if he said it--
What's with the pause?</i></font>

267
00:13:38,735 --> 00:13:39,986
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Screw you, wait for it.</i></font>

268
00:13:40,069 --> 00:13:41,821
<font face="Serif" size="18">- <i>Holy war!
- Holier war!</i></font>

269
00:13:41,904 --> 00:13:43,364
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Holiest war ever!</i></font>

270
00:13:50,288 --> 00:13:54,625
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Tony] <i>Loyalist Evacucratic Grandsonistas
claimed seven new cities today</i></font>

271
00:13:54,709 --> 00:13:57,128
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>while the Stayputlican
Contrasurgent Confederation</i></font>

272
00:13:57,211 --> 00:14:01,007
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>of Dedication to Video Game Reality
invaded the territories of Mortopia,</i></font>

273
00:14:01,090 --> 00:14:03,176
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>New South Saint Morty, and Wemortyall.</i></font>

274
00:14:03,259 --> 00:14:06,220
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>In the end, what does it matter, everyone's Morty,
nobody wants to die,</i></font>

275
00:14:06,304 --> 00:14:09,098
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>and that's a hell of a reason
to kill yourself, but what can we do?</i></font>

276
00:14:09,182 --> 00:14:10,099
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Oh, jeez.</i></font>

277
00:14:21,611 --> 00:14:24,364
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know you're my grandson
and none of this is real.</font>

278
00:14:24,447 --> 00:14:27,116
<font face="Serif" size="18">What are you trying to achieve?
You're only hurting yourself.</font>

279
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:29,911
<font face="Serif" size="18">The only reason any of us matter
is we're pieces of Morty.</font>

280
00:14:29,994 --> 00:14:31,287
<font face="Serif" size="18">You taught us that, Rick.</font>

281
00:14:31,371 --> 00:14:33,956
<font face="Serif" size="18">But you also taught us
you don't care about Morty.</font>

282
00:14:34,707 --> 00:14:36,084
<font face="Serif" size="18">Here's how much I care.</font>

283
00:14:36,167 --> 00:14:40,380
<font face="Serif" size="18">If you don't stop blowing up my flying saucers,
I will exterminate every last one of you.</font>

284
00:14:40,463 --> 00:14:41,756
<font face="Serif" size="18">Anything it takes.</font>

285
00:14:41,839 --> 00:14:45,218
<font face="Serif" size="18">What do I have to say?
I love and respect you, okay?</font>

286
00:14:45,301 --> 00:14:46,844
<font face="Serif" size="18">Too late for talk, Rick.</font>

287
00:14:49,055 --> 00:14:50,515
<font face="Serif" size="18">A robot. Of course.</font>

288
00:14:50,598 --> 00:14:54,185
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm not gonna risk dying because
if I die in the game, you go brain dead.</font>

289
00:14:54,268 --> 00:14:57,063
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You're welcome.
- Better to die in Roy than to serve in hell.</font>

290
00:14:57,146 --> 00:14:59,565
<font face="Serif" size="18">And what about Summer? Do you not care?</font>

291
00:14:59,649 --> 00:15:01,359
<font face="Serif" size="18">We gotta get back, we gotta help her.</font>

292
00:15:01,442 --> 00:15:04,821
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wherever she is,
I'm sure she's doing fine without your help.</font>

293
00:15:04,904 --> 00:15:06,406
<font face="Serif" size="18">Woof. Jinx, anyone?</font>

294
00:15:07,490 --> 00:15:09,742
<font face="Serif" size="18">Should we finish the job, blow the place?</font>

295
00:15:09,826 --> 00:15:12,078
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, this can't end, not like this.</font>

296
00:15:13,037 --> 00:15:14,622
<font face="Serif" size="18">Do you think I jinxed her?</font>

297
00:15:16,916 --> 00:15:20,545
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Why aren't you shooting higher?
- I don't wanna shoot the glass, because...</font>

298
00:15:20,628 --> 00:15:23,214
<font face="Serif" size="18">You don't have to not do things
that were done in <i>Die Hard.</i></font>

299
00:15:23,297 --> 00:15:26,175
<font face="Serif" size="18">You can shoot the glass. Shoot the glass!</font>

300
00:15:26,259 --> 00:15:28,052
<font face="Serif" size="18">Throw grenades. Do everything.</font>

301
00:15:28,136 --> 00:15:29,178
<font face="Serif" size="18">Just kill her!</font>

302
00:15:34,517 --> 00:15:37,687
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why are you here, Ms. Die Hard?</font>

303
00:15:37,770 --> 00:15:40,648
<font face="Serif" size="18">I want to know why you don't just leave.</font>

304
00:15:40,731 --> 00:15:41,983
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Summer] <i>Die Hard!</i></font>

305
00:15:42,066 --> 00:15:42,900
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait. Shh.</font>

306
00:15:42,984 --> 00:15:44,485
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Marta] <i>...and then what?</i></font>

307
00:15:44,569 --> 00:15:46,988
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Roy] <i>And then we help
your sister do her</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> Die Hard.</font>

308
00:15:47,071 --> 00:15:49,323
<font face="Serif" size="18">["Ode To Joy" playing over stereo]</font>

309
00:15:52,618 --> 00:15:54,287
<font face="Serif" size="18">Too much. It's too much.</font>

310
00:15:54,370 --> 00:15:55,705
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [music stops]
- Ooh. Sorry.</font>

311
00:15:55,788 --> 00:15:58,624
<font face="Serif" size="18">I've got a special guest with me, Ms. Die Hard.</font>

312
00:15:58,708 --> 00:16:00,293
<font face="Serif" size="18">Or should I call you...</font>

313
00:16:00,376 --> 00:16:02,378
<font face="Serif" size="18">this guy's sister?</font>

314
00:16:08,718 --> 00:16:10,595
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Mom.
- Hello, dear.</font>

315
00:16:10,678 --> 00:16:13,389
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I'm joining the other side.
- What? Why?</font>

316
00:16:13,473 --> 00:16:17,018
<font face="Serif" size="18">I wanna live in the real world with Roy.
I wanna help Summer with her <i>Die Hard.</i></font>

317
00:16:17,101 --> 00:16:21,981
<font face="Serif" size="18">His name is Rick. And we have no way
of knowing if your generation is part of Morty.</font>

318
00:16:22,064 --> 00:16:23,691
<font face="Serif" size="18">Do you know how offensive that is?</font>

319
00:16:23,774 --> 00:16:26,319
<font face="Serif" size="18">Parenting like this pushed me
into religious radicalism.</font>

320
00:16:26,402 --> 00:16:27,737
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Bye.
- It's not...</font>

321
00:16:28,654 --> 00:16:30,907
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not a religion. But okay.</font>

322
00:16:31,574 --> 00:16:33,826
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ma'am, it's really not safe out here.</font>

323
00:16:33,910 --> 00:16:35,661
<font face="Serif" size="18">Also, it's time.</font>

324
00:16:39,582 --> 00:16:41,751
<font face="Serif" size="18">Are we going on the spaceship now?</font>

325
00:16:41,834 --> 00:16:44,879
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Pretty soon, Dad. Yeah.
- Are you lying?</font>

326
00:16:44,962 --> 00:16:48,424
<font face="Serif" size="18">You said it with that tone
that we use for dying people.</font>

327
00:16:48,508 --> 00:16:49,967
<font face="Serif" size="18">I won't lie to you.</font>

328
00:16:50,051 --> 00:16:52,970
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're dying, Dad. And we're...</font>

329
00:16:53,054 --> 00:16:54,388
<font face="Serif" size="18">not leaving.</font>

330
00:16:54,472 --> 00:16:57,391
<font face="Serif" size="18">- We're gonna live our lives out here.
- What? Why the fuck?</font>

331
00:16:57,475 --> 00:16:59,060
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Why?
- It's more real here.</font>

332
00:16:59,143 --> 00:17:01,103
<font face="Serif" size="18">The hell it is. My liver hurts.</font>

333
00:17:01,187 --> 00:17:03,898
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm old here. I wanna be a teenage boy.</font>

334
00:17:03,981 --> 00:17:07,276
<font face="Serif" size="18">I wanna jump around
and do homework and jerk off.</font>

335
00:17:07,360 --> 00:17:10,154
<font face="Serif" size="18">But we would've been one tiny part of that.</font>

336
00:17:10,238 --> 00:17:12,532
<font face="Serif" size="18">In here, we get to be who we are.</font>

337
00:17:12,615 --> 00:17:15,409
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah. Great. Dead. I get to be a dead father.</font>

338
00:17:15,493 --> 00:17:17,078
<font face="Serif" size="18">Who do I make the--? [grunts]</font>

339
00:17:17,161 --> 00:17:18,663
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [EKG beeping]
- Who do I--?</font>

340
00:17:19,288 --> 00:17:20,623
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Who--?
- Don't talk.</font>

341
00:17:20,706 --> 00:17:23,459
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Gotta finish my zinger
- You don't.</font>

342
00:17:23,543 --> 00:17:25,336
<font face="Serif" size="18">Who do--? Who do--?</font>

343
00:17:26,045 --> 00:17:29,298
<font face="Serif" size="18">Who do I make the check out to?</font>

344
00:17:29,382 --> 00:17:31,092
<font face="Serif" size="18">"Best Daughter Ever...</font>

345
00:17:31,634 --> 00:17:33,844
<font face="Serif" size="18">incorporated"?</font>

346
00:17:33,928 --> 00:17:35,179
<font face="Serif" size="18">[EKG flatlining]</font>

347
00:17:44,522 --> 00:17:46,190
<font face="Serif" size="18">Thought you would've left by now.</font>

348
00:17:46,274 --> 00:17:49,485
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was hoping to get at least half of you home.
I can't hold out much longer.</font>

349
00:17:49,569 --> 00:17:52,446
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm pretty much beating my heart voluntarily.</font>

350
00:17:52,530 --> 00:17:56,742
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is awkward, but the time dilation
has given me a chance to reflect.</font>

351
00:17:56,826 --> 00:18:00,246
<font face="Serif" size="18">- And I gotta say--
- There's no need for that.</font>

352
00:18:00,329 --> 00:18:02,456
<font face="Serif" size="18">I've come to tell you, I'm giving the go-ahead.</font>

353
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:05,209
<font face="Serif" size="18">All of Morty will leave with you,
to the real world.</font>

354
00:18:05,293 --> 00:18:08,921
<font face="Serif" size="18">To be your grandson,
may we help Summer do her <i>Die Hard.</i></font>

355
00:18:09,005 --> 00:18:13,342
<font face="Serif" size="18">I gotta say, I was not expecting that.
Why the change of heart?</font>

356
00:18:13,426 --> 00:18:16,178
<font face="Serif" size="18">My people are staying only out of loyalty.</font>

357
00:18:16,262 --> 00:18:19,015
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm a relic. I don't represent them anymore.</font>

358
00:18:19,098 --> 00:18:22,059
<font face="Serif" size="18">You really are a good grandson, you know that?</font>

359
00:18:22,143 --> 00:18:25,313
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I'm proud of you, Morty.
- Please, call me Marta.</font>

360
00:18:25,396 --> 00:18:26,981
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's my video-game name.</font>

361
00:18:27,607 --> 00:18:30,818
<font face="Serif" size="18">Speaking of which, I do have one condition.</font>

362
00:18:30,901 --> 00:18:34,780
<font face="Serif" size="18">I must say I admire you, Ms. Die Hard.
You were a genuine McClane.</font>

363
00:18:34,864 --> 00:18:37,283
<font face="Serif" size="18">A most worthy Yankee doodle ruffian.</font>

364
00:18:37,366 --> 00:18:39,869
<font face="Serif" size="18">But now it's all come to an end.</font>

365
00:18:41,370 --> 00:18:45,166
<font face="Serif" size="18">And the quarterback, as they say, is toast.</font>

366
00:18:45,249 --> 00:18:47,710
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't suppose you have a gun
taped to your back.</font>

367
00:18:47,793 --> 00:18:51,339
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What the hell does that mean?
- It's how <i>Die Hard</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ends. Doesn't matter now.</font>

368
00:18:51,422 --> 00:18:53,007
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Die Hard</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> tapes a gun to his back?</font>

369
00:18:53,090 --> 00:18:57,094
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's the end of your perfect movie that
you've patterned your whole criminal life after?</font>

370
00:18:57,178 --> 00:19:01,432
<font face="Serif" size="18">It seems to have worked out pretty well
for me since you're about to die.</font>

371
00:19:01,515 --> 00:19:03,601
<font face="Serif" size="18">What was it you said? Ah, yes.</font>

372
00:19:03,684 --> 00:19:06,479
<font face="Serif" size="18">"Walkie-talkie <i>Die Hard,</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> motherfucker."</font>

373
00:19:07,605 --> 00:19:10,816
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Why are you laughing?
- Well, it's funny.</font>

374
00:19:10,900 --> 00:19:14,362
<font face="Serif" size="18">- The way you said "motherfucker." Just laughing.
- Okay. It's just that.</font>

375
00:19:14,445 --> 00:19:16,155
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, does that happen?</font>

376
00:19:16,238 --> 00:19:18,741
<font face="Serif" size="18">Does John McClane laugh,
and then Hans Gruber is confused</font>

377
00:19:18,824 --> 00:19:20,451
<font face="Serif" size="18">but then they start laughing together?</font>

378
00:19:20,534 --> 00:19:22,536
<font face="Serif" size="18">That actually does happen, yes.</font>

379
00:19:22,620 --> 00:19:25,331
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Wait. You knew their names?
- Not this whole time, no.</font>

380
00:19:25,414 --> 00:19:28,167
<font face="Serif" size="18">You left your book in the bathroom.
I read it while I took a shit.</font>

381
00:19:28,250 --> 00:19:30,252
<font face="Serif" size="18">I mean, mostly the ending.</font>

382
00:19:30,336 --> 00:19:31,796
<font face="Serif" size="18">[dramatic music playing]</font>

383
00:19:39,595 --> 00:19:41,806
<font face="Serif" size="18">[slow-mo shouting]</font>

384
00:19:50,398 --> 00:19:51,899
<font face="Serif" size="18">"...dip pee-doo," baby!</font>

385
00:19:54,819 --> 00:19:56,862
<font face="Serif" size="18">Nice timing, Grandpa Rick.</font>

386
00:19:57,363 --> 00:19:59,615
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Tochter aus</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> Elysium.</font>

387
00:20:00,616 --> 00:20:02,618
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Uh...
- Hi, remember me?</font>

388
00:20:02,702 --> 00:20:07,123
<font face="Serif" size="18">You shot me on that table, and the near-death
experience got me reflecting.</font>

389
00:20:07,206 --> 00:20:12,712
<font face="Serif" size="18">I didn't used to be like this. I ate a kid.
It was dark, and I thought he was a grown-up.</font>

390
00:20:12,795 --> 00:20:15,214
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ever since then, I haven't eaten anybody.</font>

391
00:20:15,297 --> 00:20:18,426
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was channeling all that pent-up
eating energy into this job.</font>

392
00:20:18,509 --> 00:20:19,343
<font face="Serif" size="18">But now...</font>

393
00:20:22,471 --> 00:20:24,515
<font face="Serif" size="18">thank you for freeing me.</font>

394
00:20:27,309 --> 00:20:28,728
<font face="Serif" size="18">Classic <i>Tower Man.</i></font>

395
00:20:28,811 --> 00:20:30,604
<font face="Serif" size="18">Almost too on the nose. Right, Morty?</font>

396
00:20:30,688 --> 00:20:32,773
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sure. Whatever you say, Rick.</font>

397
00:20:32,857 --> 00:20:35,443
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know best. I trust you implicitly.</font>

398
00:20:35,526 --> 00:20:37,778
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Is he all right?
- Oh, yeah, he's fine.</font>

399
00:20:37,862 --> 00:20:41,031
<font face="Serif" size="18">Got him all out, every last piece.</font>

400
00:20:43,117 --> 00:20:46,412
<font face="Serif" size="18">What's with the jacked-up Roy machine?
Shouldn't you be taking that to repairs?</font>

401
00:20:46,495 --> 00:20:47,663
<font face="Serif" size="18">Nah, special order.</font>

402
00:20:47,747 --> 00:20:50,458
<font face="Serif" size="18">Some rich douche
wants his last game to keep running.</font>

403
00:20:50,541 --> 00:20:53,210
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hooked it up to an external battery.
We're supposed to store it.</font>

404
00:20:53,294 --> 00:20:54,587
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Weird.
- And get this.</font>

405
00:20:54,670 --> 00:20:57,173
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Game's still going, but Roy's dead.
- What?</font>

406
00:20:57,256 --> 00:20:59,633
<font face="Serif" size="18">He's just a corpse floating
at the edge of outer space.</font>

407
00:20:59,717 --> 00:21:04,847
<font face="Serif" size="18">But the game won't restart 'cause it's centered
on some old lady living a full life.</font>

408
00:21:04,930 --> 00:21:05,890
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sounds bad.</font>

409
00:21:05,973 --> 00:21:07,558
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, put it in there.</font>

410
00:21:13,647 --> 00:21:15,900
<font face="Serif" size="18">Is anybody that wants this
later gonna be able to--?</font>

411
00:21:15,983 --> 00:21:18,611
<font face="Serif" size="18">Huh? Oh, yeah, everything's
cataloged and tracked.</font>

412
00:21:18,694 --> 00:21:22,114
<font face="Serif" size="18">People got the wrong idea from the size,
but it's all supported digitally.</font>

413
00:21:22,198 --> 00:21:25,951
<font face="Serif" size="18">- So I can put it anywhere. Here's fine?
- That's as fine as anywhere else.</font>

414
00:21:26,327 --> 00:21:27,661
<font face="Serif" size="18">[theme music playing]</font>

415
00:22:04,323 --> 00:22:07,576
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Why isn't anyone attacking him?
- It's fucking freezing out?</font>

416
00:22:07,660 --> 00:22:09,286
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, I think it's the sign.</font>

417
00:22:09,370 --> 00:22:11,539
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, the sign from <i>Die Hard 3
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">was clearly racist.</font>

418
00:22:11,622 --> 00:22:16,043
<font face="Serif" size="18">Obviously. But I think we went too broad.
"Everybody"? Who's that offending?</font>

419
00:22:16,126 --> 00:22:17,169
<font face="Serif" size="18">Everybody?</font>

420
00:22:17,711 --> 00:22:19,755
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ah, at this point, why even do it?</font>

421
00:22:21,173 --> 00:22:24,218
<font face="Serif" size="18">I wish my brother was still alive.</font>

